**Title:** Send Email with Tier-Specific Fulfillment Guidelines

**As a** warehouse supervisor,  
**I want** to receive a templated email with product-specific fulfillment instructions based on the subscription tier,  
**So that** I can ensure packing consistency and minimize mistakes.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] Fulfillment email is triggered only for orders with a subscription tag
- [ ] Email includes packing notes (e.g., cold pack for Deluxe tier serum)
- [ ] Email is sent to warehouse@lunaluxenaturals.com with order # and due date
